abstract: >-
  AI Project Standard is a reusable repository template and reference
  implementation for adopting Open Source and/or Human-AI Collaboration
  standards. Three profiles (OSS-only, AI-only, Combined) share one
  repository and one version stream, with multi-tool pointer files for
  Claude Code, OpenAI Codex, GitHub Copilot, and Cursor.
